{"type": "excalidraw", "version": 2, "source": "excalidraw-diagram-skill", "elements": [{"type": "rectangle", "id": "darkbg", "x": -4000, "y": -3000, "width": 10000, "height": 7500, "backgroundColor": "#1e1e2e", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "transparent", "strokeWidth": 0, "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100}, {"type": "text", "id": "title1", "x": 20, "y": 10, "width": 380, "height": 28, "text": "HTML  JSX  이유", "fontSize": 20, "strokeColor": "#e5e5e5", "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "opacity": 100}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "box2", "x": 20, "y": 45, "width": 380.0, "height": 228, "backgroundColor": "#1e3a5f", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#4a9eed", "strokeWidth": 2, "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "roundness": {"type": 3}}, {"type": "text", "id": "txt3", "x": 35, "y": 60, "width": 350, "height": 198, "text": "class  className  class는 JS 예약어\nfor  htmlFor  for는 JS 예약어\ntabindex  tabIndex  camelCase 규칙\nonclick  onClick  camelCase 규칙\nonchange  onChange  camelCase 규칙\nmaxlength  maxLength  camelCase 규칙\nstyle=\"...\"  style={{...}}  객체 형태로 전달\nchecked (HTML)  defaultChecked  비제어 컴포넌트\nvalue (HTML)  defaultValue  비제어 컴포넌트", "fontSize": 14, "strokeColor": "#e5e5e5", "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "middle", "opacity": 100, "containerId": "box2"}], "appState": {"viewBackgroundColor": "#1e1e2e"}}